NEWS                                                            -*- outline -*-
----

Welcome to lockdev 1.0.4.  Please read these release notes carefully.

Full installation instructions are provided in the INSTALL file.  The
README file also contains more specific notes regarding building and
configuration.

* Major changes in 1.0.4:

  1) Outstanding patches from RedHat and SUSE have been merged.

  2) The build system has been converted to use the autotools,
     rather than custom Makefiles.
